title: Bigfish Undiscovered World: The Incan Sun - RaBBiT
description:
Undiscovered World: The Incan Sun

Stranded on an uncharted island, a haunting family mystery that stretches back decades begins to unravel before you. In order to find a way off this rock, you must join the quest to prove the legend of the Incan Sun. Venture deep into the dense jungle, piece together hidden artifacts and solve challenging mini-games to uncover the truth behind this ancient mystery.

    * Stunning Hidden Object Scenes.
    * Challenging Mini-Games.
    * Three modes of game play.
